<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.5">
<l>tiṟampāmaṉ maṇkākkiṉṟēṉ yāṉē yeṉṉun tiṟampāmaṉ malaiyeṭut tēṉē yeṉṉun</l>
<l>tiṟampāma lacuraraikkoṉ ṟēṉē yeṉṉun tiṟaṅkāṭṭi yaṉṟaivaraik kāttēṉē yeṉṉun</l>
<l>tiṟampāmaṟ kaṭalkaṭain tēṉē yeṉṉun tiṟampāta kaṭalvaṇṇa ṉēṟak kolō</l>
<l>tiṟampāta vulakat tīrkkeṉ collukēṉ tiṟampā teṉṟiru makaḷey tiṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Unswervingly I protect the earth”, she says,</l>
	<l>“Unswervingly I lifted the mountain”, she says,</l>
<l>“Unswervingly I killed the Asuras”, she says,</l>
	<l>“Showing [them] the doctrine that day I protected the Five”, she says,</l>
<l>“Unswervingly I churned the ocean”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the unswerving one of ocean-colour takes possession of [her]?</l>
<l>What can I say to the unswerving world,</l>
	<l>[words that also] would reach unswervingly my precious daughter?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
